    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. Mechanically, it is sound; the engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts as expected without any hesitation. The exterior is clean and presents well, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper from normal use. Inside, the upholstery is in great shape with no tears, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. All electronics and climate control systems are fully functional. This is a solid, reliable car that is ready for its next owner with no immediate repairs needed.",
      "price": 34000.0,
