    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor dings, and some paint fading on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows significant wear and some staining, and while the engine runs steadily, it may require some minor maintenance like a tune-up or brake pad replacement in the near future. It is a solid, functional car for someone looking for transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
