    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained to the highest possible standards. This example represents the pinnacle of its class, boasting a pristine exterior and a flawless interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this vehicle offers an unparalleled ownership experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
